snippet.title: Shop Tycoon: Prepare your wallet - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Shop Tycoon is a store simulator from Airem, the creator of Hovercars 3077: Underground. Create a supermarket, sex shop, games store or a store with good Polish vodka. Place your logo, hire employees, expand your car fleet, build offices and parking lots, create a chain of stores and more!

Developed by Airem
